@12299  = ~In order to have the proper amount of proficiencies, using this tome will remove all of the character's current proficiencies and then begin a dialogue which will allow the character to choose new ones.

NOTE: this should be used right away (or not at all). If the character levels up and advances a proficiency, it will prevent this tome from granting the correct number of proficiency points.

If you also have a tome enabling you to change your class and kit, you should decide whether you want to use that tome or this one. Each will make the other one disappear.
~
