@12311  = ~Leadership~
@12312  = ~Leadership: a warrior in this posture may supervise and direct those around <PRO_HIMHER>, resulting in a 1-point bonus to attack rolls, armor class, and spellcasting speed for all party members within 20 feet.~
@12313  = ~Grappling~
@12314  = ~Grappling: when using this posture, each round, both the attacker and the nearest melee enemy will be rooted in place for three seconds. If the enemy fails a save vs. breath, they will be Slowed for one round.~
@12315  = ~Precise Strike~
@12316  = ~Precise Strike: when using this posture, an attacker will make critical hits on rolls of 19 or 20, instead of just 20.~
