@12318  = ~Reckless Attack: when using this posture, an attacker will make an extra attack every two rounds (+0.5 APR), but will suffer a 3-point penalty to attack rolls.~
@12319  = ~Fighting Dirty~
@12320  = ~Fighting Dirty: when using this posture, up to once per round, an attacker can briefly trip, blind, or weaken a nearby attacker, if the attacker fails a save vs. Breath Weapon.~
