@12325  = ~Spell Evasion~
@12326  = ~Spell Evasion: when using this posture and targeted by a spell that can be evaded (Fireball, Lightning Bolt, etc.), as long as the character is not helpless (e.g. held, stunned, asleep, etc.) the effects may be completely avoided upon a successful save vs. Breath.~
